{
  "events": [
    {
      "offset_seconds": 0,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 46,
      "description": "Static image of a math problem: 'Which quantity is proportional to 15/3?'"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 46,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "description": "View switches to a live screen share of a student's desktop showing MobyMax and a floating Zoom window.",
      "details": "Student name 'Mykael Baez' visible in MobyMax; Zoom participant name 'oswald'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 48.3,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "How's it going?",
      "speaker_name": "Paisley Crawford"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 50.1,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "It's going good.",
      "speaker_name": "Mykael"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 51.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Good. Do you have any questions?",
      "speaker_name": "Paisley Crawford"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 54.2,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Um, no not really.",
      "speaker_name": "Mykael"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 56.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay. Well, I'm just gonna hang out here for a few minutes. If you think of anything, you can ask.",
      "speaker_name": "Paisley Crawford"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 61.3,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "speaker_name": "Mykael"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 62,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 93,
      "description": "Student is idle on the MobyMax screen. Background classroom noise is audible."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 155,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Play button",
      "details": "Clicks the audio play button to read the question."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 158,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 7,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "[Text-to-Speech] Evan purchased 3 1/2 kilograms of cashews for $49. What is the price per kilogram?"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 174,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Text input box"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 176,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "0.3",
      "details": "Types '0.3' into the answer field."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 180,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Next arrow button"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 180,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "'Try Again' notification appears."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 181,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "14",
      "details": "Deletes previous input and types '14'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 196,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Next arrow button"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 196,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "description": "Incorrect answer feedback displayed. Shows correct answer: $14.00."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 200,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Next arrow button",
      "details": "Dismisses feedback modal."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 205,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Next problem loads on MobyMax: 'Katrina purchased 8 1/4 ounces...'"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 207.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Well at least you know now for next time.",
      "speaker_name": "Paisley Crawford"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 210.3,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 0.8,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Mmhmm.",
      "speaker_name": "Mykael"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 212,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 44,
      "description": "No action on screen. Student looks down/away."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 256,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Screen goes black momentarily."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 257,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "View returns to MobyMax. A new problem is visible: 'You bought 0.40 lb of spinach...'"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 295.3,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Do you need help?",
      "speaker_name": "Paisley Crawford"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 304.2,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "No, I'm good.",
      "speaker_name": "Mykael"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 306.1,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay, no worries. Let me know if you need anything.",
      "speaker_name": "Paisley Crawford"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 309.1,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yup.",
      "speaker_name": "Mykael"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 311,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 52,
      "description": "Student sits silently looking at the screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 363,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "to_app": "Chrome",
      "to_window": "New Tab",
      "details": "Student opens a new browser tab."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 364,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "ity is proportional to 8/12",
      "details": "Types partial query into Google search bar."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 365,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Search suggestion",
      "details": "Clicks suggestion: 'which quanity is proportional to 8/12...'"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 366,
      "event_type": "page_scroll",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "direction": "down",
      "details": "Scrolls down through Google search results."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 369,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Image Result",
      "details": "Clicks on an image result from Brainly."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 395,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "description": "View switches back to Zoom active speaker view (Tutor). Screen sharing ends."
    }
  ]
}
